PMID: 34418461 [Indexed for MEDLINE]


556. BMC Cancer. 2021 Aug 21;21(1):944. doi: 10.1186/s12885-021-08638-2.

Optimizing oropharyngeal cancer management by using proton beam therapy: trends 
of cost-effectiveness.

Li G(1), Xia YF(2)(3), Huang YX(4), Okat D(5), Qiu B(2)(3), Doyen J(6)(7), 
